{"tid":1309340,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"對唔住 吉野家 我睇錯左你","createTime":"2019-07-12T07:02:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-14T04:10:40.000Z","uid":142358,"like":56,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"58a3257582c25803524725cdf175ce7c6f3faaf2","tid":1309340,"uid":142358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T07:02:49.000Z","msg":"我對自己曾經開過吉野家打手post感到好羞恥。上次獅子狗個post完左，我同自己講，果然無睇錯呢間咁有良知嘅餐廳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />但係之後相信大家都知道發生咩事<br />\n<br />\n我真係好唔捨得溫泉玉子牛肉飯，唯有希望有其他地方可以再食過<br />\n<br />\n咁樣講啦，飯食完可以再整過，有啲嘢失去左就攞唔返"},{"pid":"bb2554b5a9cb69971209807f0987a10439b8307b","tid":1309340,"uid":202137,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T07:04:01.000Z","msg":"去日本食囉"},{"pid":"b180ff0f701c3f242a5763f4b43880345acff68f","tid":1309340,"uid":142358,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T07:05:04.000Z","msg":"有去啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc62135ff12695e96f86a9ab4246e6083d2b2ec7","tid":1309340,"uid":142358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bb2554b5a9cb69971209807f0987a10439b8307b","tid":1309340,"uid":202137,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T07:04:01.000Z","msg":"去日本食囉"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T07:05:57.000Z","msg":"日本個生蛋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"480c263eb88d6098b691596f5a19bdbb839b2c1a","tid":1309340,"uid":69746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T07:13:44.000Z","msg":"求人不如求己 自己整<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c2086fd755e4371044c1133a7b3dff6a3da9af9","tid":1309340,"uid":165336,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T07:14:40.000Z","msg":"杜汶澤公司同吉野家合興真係相映成趣<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1309339\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1309339</a>"},{"pid":"5d2e8e110ef90d9a58ea